[color=yellow][heading]GENERAL[/heading]
Personally, I didn\'t think my nord warrior would enjoy staying in Severin manor very much, so I made this. Brunnsheim is a quaint little player home, located in the Skaal village. It features the classic whiterunesque architecture, which it shares with its neighbours, but with just a touch of mainland.[/color]
[color=green][heading]GOOD TO KNOW[/heading]
* This mod requires the DRAGONBORN DLC to function.
[/color]
[heading]WHAT WE HAVE SO FAR[/heading] [color=yellow]
[list] [*] An open Living and Dining area, similar to the one of Breezehome, but hand crafted;
[*] An Enchanting laboratory;
[*] A Pantry;
[*] Master Bedroom;
[*] Follower Bedroom;
[*] A dining nook on top of the loft;
[*] Bookcases with a joint capacity of storing and displaying 58 books,
[*] 6 weapon displays + 1 Dagger display case
[*] 1 Safe, 2 general storage chests, and 1 safe to store Knapsack [/list]
[/color][heading]Update Log[/heading]

-Version 1.0
